headline: Access Advance Announces Major Growth in Its HEVC and VVC Patent Pools
summary: BOSTON, November 24, 2025--Access Advance LLC today announced significant expansions of both its HEVC Advance and VVC Advance Patent Pools during the second and third quarters of 2025, underscoring continued industry confidence in the company's balanced and transparent approach to video codec licensing.
